              "id": "QUE59077",
              "question": "Curtis attends a local college where he studies sociology. During the week, he works at the school library and attends classes. On the weekends, he enjoys spending time with his close friends from high school and going out with them to meet new people at clubs. Which of the following would be considered Curtis’s primary social group?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
