                  "score": 0.0,
                  "response": "sider this: Primary groups are characterized by intimate, long-term, face-to-face relationships. Curtis’ relationship with coworkers are not intimate. LO 6.2 Discuss the main characteristics of primary groups, secondary groups, in-groups and out-groups, reference groups, and social networks."
                },
                "answer_2": {
